advancement.takumicraft.root.desc:
Going into Chaotic Creeper World! 
 Get damaged from explosion.
advancement.takumicraft.root.title: Takumi Craft
advancement.takumicraft.slay_all.title: All Complete
entity.takumicraft.arrowcreeper.desc: Hundreds of thousand of arrows, to destroy you.
entity.takumicraft.bangcreeper.desc: This explosion can even destroy obsidian. There's no way to protect you.
entity.takumicraft.childcreeper.desc: Carring the love in their bodies, and not afraid to explode in order to protect their own children.
entity.takumicraft.coppercreeper.desc: A creeper with copper metalic luster. Too unbated, too strong.
entity.takumicraft.cowcreeper.desc: A creeper looks like a cow. Not provide a milk, but explosion.
entity.takumicraft.diamondcreeper.desc: A creeper with diamond heart. Too hard, too strong.
entity.takumicraft.dirtcreeper.desc: Destroy dirt. The ground will be filled with this explosion like a earthquake.
entity.takumicraft.drownedcreeper.desc: Danger from the sea, deeper than the cave.
entity.takumicraft.emeraldcreeper.desc: A creeper with emerald toughness. Too big, too strong.
entity.takumicraft.endercreeper.desc: Warp you to somewhere, no one knows where. you might enjoy the trip :)
entity.takumicraft.fallcreeper.desc: All things fallen. Blocks, entities, even this game fall and shut down...
entity.takumicraft.firecreeper.desc: As soon as it explode, the forest is going to be burnt. Stop it!
entity.takumicraft.happinesscreeper.desc: Heal or destroy? This cause a huge explosion heal you.
entity.takumicraft.huskcreeper.desc: Desert zombie creeper. You will suffer of  hunger
entity.takumicraft.icecreeper.desc: Pack you into ice. Burn it by fire? No,frozen ice can freeze even fire.
entity.takumicraft.ironcreeper.desc: A creeper with iron compactness. Too small, too strong.
entity.takumicraft.lavacreeper.desc: Lava press you like Tsunami, not to be burnt, you must cold with water.
entity.takumicraft.lightcreeper.desc: Destroy light, it is enough that the light is only one, this creeper.
entity.takumicraft.naturalcreeper.desc: Good for nature... no, no, the good look tree contains explosive!
entity.takumicraft.patinacreeper.desc: A creeper with copper metalic rust. Too bated, too brittle.
entity.takumicraft.phantomcreeper.desc: A flying nightmare, shows a phantom of fighter from the air.
entity.takumicraft.redstonecreeper.desc: A creeper with redstone speed. Too fast, too strong.
entity.takumicraft.sandcreeper.desc: Explosion sandwich you in sand, soon only your items rise up.
entity.takumicraft.silentcreeper.desc: It came nearby you, without sound. It is too late if you notice.
entity.takumicraft.slimecreeper.desc: It is called 'CreeperClusterBomb', consecutive, large slimy explosion.
entity.takumicraft.stonecreeper.desc: Destroy stones. The cave will be filled with this explosion like a storm.
entity.takumicraft.watercreeper.desc: Water flood, don't stay in water! To breathe, you have to swim up.
entity.takumicraft.woodcreeper.desc: Destroy woods. The forest will be filled with this explosion like a burning.
entity.takumicraft.zombiecreeper.desc: They attack villager, with the explosion changes them to zombie creeper.
entity.takumicraft.zombievillagercreeper: Villager changed zombie, attacks friends, not knowing who they are.
takumicraft.config.isdebugmode: RECOMMEND TO SET THIS FALSE, this config is only for TakumiCraft debugger.
